texts.text: Impede me any further and you risk losing your lives.
Apsaras, you are a water nymph.
Robbing you of your water, these humans' source of life, must feel considerably worse...
But if you continue being a thorn in my side as such,
I will have no choice but to unleash my full wrath upon you.
My water... It is... Life itself...
I must do this... Even if it...!
Huh? Yo, I feel heaps better...!
I see. She is indeed a water nymph and acts accordingly.
I shared the water within me with the rest of you.
I am a water nymph. I can control at least small amounts of water.
But if Vritra attacks us in the same manner once more...
I doubt that I will have enough water to save you all.
You must defeat Vritra right here, right now.
>Apsaras begins transforming into a clear ball of water.
I must do this to fulfill my promise to Indra.
Don't clam up on me. Say something!
Hm? You dare invade the sanctity of my body...?
>You then hear Apsaras whispering into your ear.
I will show you where to attack momentarily...!
Yes, I see. It's a sort of focal point.
It's a nexus of muscles, but it can also be a weak spot.
All of the water Vritra stole is concentrated there.
Strike this spot and you may be able to breach it like a dam...!
Apsaras, my body is not your plaything...!
Yo, is Vritra losin' control of himself?!
It's Apsaras! She's doing this to him...!
Now! We have to attack now, everyone!
It's not working. He's too tough...!
If only we could reach inside him...!
We can use that special technique you taught me...!
The one that does damage to someone's internal organs?
If we can strike at the water inside him,
we may be able to break him.
Secret tai chi technique, Gut Buster!
Hang on! You're attacking him directly?! Not with your demons?!
>Jeng Yun performs a palm strike on Vritra's gut!
>Some water spills out of Vritra's mouth.

*Groan*
No child is going to defeat me!
Shit, he's doin' that thing again! We're done for if we let him!
And my technique wasn't good enough it seems...
No, it definitely worked! Tell your demons to do the same thing!
>Your demons strike at Vritra's gut repeatedly!
>He also loses control of his body!
Apsaras, can you attack him for us from within?!
>The Liberators strike at the same time as Apsaras,
>and attack Vritra from inside and out...!
